      "title": "Deepening fuel crisis; No schools next week too",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Education Ministry has decided to declare next week (July 4 to July 8) as a holiday week for all government and state-approved private schools owing to the current fuel crisis.",
        "The Ministry said the school time lost during next week will be covered in the next school vacation term.\u00a0(DSB)"
      ],
